ji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:07:48.000Z","msg":"陳小姐認為，「如果你個商場根本就冇呢啲人流，去support你嘅營運，咁佢憑乜嘢收我咁多租呢。」<br />\n<br />\non撚9<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 簽左約架嘛柒頭 係到發悔氣<br />\n咁撚多野講 唔好租囉傻閪<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T18:08:44.000Z","msg":"又你又佢咁 講野都9唔搭8<br />\n你個商場 但係佢收租?"},{"pid":"5ed351b22489909e4a5d1cec487301415cd0bdfc","tid":1815721,"uid":252492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:18:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53c647ab9a1632a24a85472446e78bf98f8d3a6e","tid":1815721,"uid":32588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:21:55.000Z","msg":"無提長實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e3f3f280dbdbcd1663e46e5e637fda1e027a44e6","tid":1815721,"uid":52972,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:39:23.000Z","msg":"新地就租金問題接受本報查詢時回應指，明白近月的社會事件中，商場商戶受到不同程度的影響，而新地一直與商戶保持緊密聯繫，主動提供協助，包括<span style=\"color: red;\">增聘不少人手加強保安、盡快修復被破壞的設施、協助商舖盡快恢復營業等</span>。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">即係無減</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n另外，新地又指，旗下部分商場曾全日暫停營業，雖然此舉旨在保障顧客、商戶及職員的安全，但新地已寬減該些受影響商戶<span style=\"color: red;\">當日</span>的租金及其他相關費用，期望能紓緩商戶經營壓力，共渡時艱。新地亦推行了各項措施，盡力改善營商環境；並會按個別商戶的實際狀況，提供各種適切的紓困措施。<br />\n<span style=\"color: green;\">當日的租金， 真係多撚謝。</span>"},{"pid":"d879d76614446778139ae47328b4755c0a4ecab1","tid":1815721,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:45:11.000Z","msg":"唔好減呀<br />\n死頂啦<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"feac9a28633cbd48cefa5384639b2bd29da2b045","tid":1815721,"uid":191926,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T02:46:53.000Z"